        </div>
        <div class="achievement-text">
          <h3>Outstanding Academic Performance</h3>
          <p>Our students have achieved remarkable success in the CHSE examinations, with over 95% pass rate and many securing top positions in their respective streams.</p>
          <p style="text-align:center;margin-top:1rem;font-weight:bold;color:#f97316;">Congratulations to all our meritorious students!</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="donate" data-aos="fade-up">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="column">
          <h2>Student Donation Information</h2>
          <p>KASH student sponsorship programs provide financial and educational support to students from economically weaker backgrounds. Each contribution helps cover tuition, food, lodging, and academic materials.</p>
          <div class="donation-stats">
            <div class="stat-item">
              <strong>₹15,000</strong>
              <span>Annual Education Cost</span>
            </div>
